                                        <div class="uc-content ">
                                            <h5 style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><strong>Be informed about the main issues!</strong></span></h5>
                                            <p style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</p>
                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Most people play for pleasure and enjoy moderate participation in games within their financial capacity. However, for a small percentage of people gambling is not a form of entertainment and this is a challenge that must be considered seriously.</span></span></p>
